comments:
That part which until 1.4.1922 formed the 
    parishes of St. George Hanover Square, St. Margaret & St. John and the Close 
    of the Collegiate Church of St. Peter, together with the small part of the former 
    parish of St. Martin in the Fields in the Victoria ward of the City of Westminster 
    Metropolitan Borough. See also Table 2, note (h).
